Package org.gradle.api.artifacts.dsl

Interface PlatformDependencyModifiers

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Dependencies
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    JvmComponentDependencies
    @Incubating
public interface PlatformDependencyModifiers
extends Dependencies
    Dependency APIs for using Platforms in dependencies blocks.

    NOTE: This API is incubating and is likely to change until it's made stable.

    Since:
    7.6
